README FOR BUILDING SigmetUdDsr
===============================

This applicartion needs the Sigmet includes installed.

1. Download includes from Sigmet ftp site
-----------------------------------------

ftp ftp.sigmet.com

log in as anonymous, use email as password

cd (for example) to 

  outgoing/releases/8.12.5/RHEL5/rda

Get the headers:

  get headers.tgz

2. Install headers
------------------

  tar xvfz headers.tgz
  sudo mkdir /usr/sigmet
  sudo cp -r include /usr/sigmet


